<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 1 (Zelos) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>クレス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cless</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>チェスター</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Chester</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ゼロス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Zelos</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ロイド</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Lloyd</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>勝負に負けてしまった以上、仕方ないね。
ファンタジアの主人公の座は
ゼロスに譲る事にするよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I lost this battle, so there's nothing more
to be done about it. I yield the role of
Phantasia's protagonist to Zelos.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おい！　マジでいいのかよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey! Are you really okay with that?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いいのかもなにも、決定事項だからね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It doesn't matter if he's okay with it.
This matter is settled.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やったな、ゼロス！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You did it, Zelos!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あとは任せたよ、ゼロス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I leave the rest to you, Zelos.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあさっそく、ダジャレの練習からだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In which case, you have to start off
by practicing your puns.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……へ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Huh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ファンタジアの主人公の条件は
ダジャレが達者な事だからね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's a condition of being Phantasia's protagonist
that you have to be skilled with puns.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>当然ゼロスも爆笑必至の
ダジャレを連発してくれないと</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So naturally, it's a necessity for you to
make puns in rapid succession and
bring about  bursts of laughter.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だ、ダジャレ……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>P-Puns...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>嫌だ！　そんなのモテねぇじゃんよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heck no! That's NOT gonna
make me more popular!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Unreferenced</Section>
